      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Anguish at Gracie Mansion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Bruce Donnola letter on May 11 article on Mayor Rudolph Giuliani's marital separation says public's Clinton fatigue has now been replaced with Giuliani fatigue</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Yep, it's official: My Clinton fatigue has now been replaced with Giuliani fatigue (front page, May 11).</p>
        <p>BRUCE DONNOLA  Brooklyn, May 11, 2000</p>
      </block>
